modules.description: This module implements a constant database (CDB) format for efficient key-value data storage and retrieval. It provides functions to build a CDB file by adding key-value pairs, iterate over all entries, and search for values by key in an open CDB file. The primary data structures are `cdb_creator` for writing and `cdb_file` for reading, supporting use cases such as creating immutable lookup tables and performing fast key-based queries.
